     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       hw t b lss bsy n  bsy bsy wrld
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       <img alt="" src="http://mnmlist.com/fotos/20090911busy.jpg"/>
       <small>
        Pht crtsy f
        <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/jamesjordan/875829317/">
         Jms Jrdn
        </a>
        .
       </small>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/about/#leo">
        By L
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       Mst f s r prtty bsy, jst bt vry dy.
      </p>
      <p>
       Sm lk t tht wy — bng bsy s lmst  stts symbl, s t shws y’r mprtnt nd prdctv nd  g-gttr nd chvr. If y’r n  pwr mtng nd sndng mls n yr Blckbrry nd mkng clls, y mst b mprtnt, rght?
      </p>
      <p>
       I sy w shld rjct tht lttl gm f wh’s bsr thn whm. W shld pt t. W shld sy, “I’d rthr fnd pc f mnd, nd b bl t rlx, nd rlly njy lf, thn llw t t pss m by jst s I cn b ‘prdctv’ nd shw vryn hw mprtnt I m.”
      </p>
      <p>
       <span class="caps">
        OK,
       </span>
       myb sy smthng shrtr nstd. Lk, “N thnks.”
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Why bsy s  fl’s trp
       </strong>
       <br/>
       Thng wth bsy s, t nvr nds. Y’ll nvr gt t f t (nlss y mk  vry cnscs ffrt), bcs thr s n nd t th t-d lst, th mls, th IMs nd phn clls, th mtngs nd mtngs nd ys, mr mtngs. W’r hmstrs n  trdmll, rnnng fr n rl prps, xcpt t mk  bss hppy, t mk mny fr smn ls, r prhps t mk mny fr rslvs … bt t wht nd?
      </p>
      <p>
       Th trdmll wll nvr nd. Thr s nvr n nd, bcs thr s n dstntn.
       <br/>
       <span id="more-282">
       </span>
       <br/>
       Bt gss wht? Th jrny
       <em>
        s
       </em>
       th dstntn. W r lrdy thr — wht w d tdy s wht r lf s, wht t’s ll bt. Is bng ths bsy rlly th mnng f lf? Or s thr smthng mr? Is thr  bttr lf?
      </p>
      <p>
       I blv w shld schw bsy-nss fr thngs wth mr vl. Eschw th rgnt fr th mprtnt. And vn thn, f w’r dng mprtnt thngs, w shld nt fll vry mnt wth mprtnt thngs. W nd t lrn t rlx, nd b hppy, nd njy lf. Othrws, t’s nt wrth lvng.
      </p>
      <p>
       W nd t rdscvr wht t’s lk t
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2007/03/the-art-of-doing-nothing/">
        d nthng
       </a>
       ,
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2009/07/be-still/">
        t st stll
       </a>
       , t
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2008/09/sound-of-silence-how-to-find-some-quietude-in-your-life/">
        njy slnc
       </a>
       . W nd t pt mr spc n btwn thngs, nstd f crmmng thm tgthr ll th tm. Lt’s stp bng bsy, nd strt bng hppy.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Hw t b lss bsy
       </strong>
       <br/>
       It strts wth  dcsn: I wnt t b lss bsy. I dn’t wnt t d ths nymr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wht fllws rlly dpnds n hw mch cntrl y hv vr yr dy.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        If y hv t lst sm cntrl
       </strong>
       : Mk tw lsts: yr dl dy, nd ll th thngs tht fll p yr dy (ll yr cmmtmnts). Strt by lmntng cmmtmnts tht r nt ssntl, tht dn’t mk p yr dl dy — cll r ml ppl nd tll thm y cn n lngr cmmt t th cmmtmnt, tht y dn’t hv th tm. Ppl wll b dsppntd bt wll lv.
      </p>
      <p>
       Thn strt fllwng yr dl schdl. B sr thr’s spcs btwn thngs, s y’r nt rshd. Lv lrg blcks f tm wd pn, s y cn fcs n crtng r dng wht mks y hppy. Lv t lst n bg blck fr dng nn-wrk stff, whthr tht’s spndng tm wth fmly, r xrcsng, r dng  hbby, r jst rlxng.
      </p>
      <p>
       Lk t yr t-d lst nd s wht y cn lmnt r dlgt r pstpn ntl ltr. Ech dy, jst chs n r thr thngs t fcs n. Hv  blck f tm dsgntd fr dng mls nd phn clls nd smllr tsks, s thy dn’t ntrrpt y thrght th dy.
      </p>
      <p>
       Dscnnct frm th Intrnt fr lrg chnks f tm. Whn y g plcs, trn yr mbl dvc ff, r lv t bhnd, s y cn b dscnnctd frm th nln wrld nd ntrrptns, nd cnnctd t th rl wrld nd rl ppl. Clr wy dstrctns nd ntrrptns s y’r nt lwys swtchng yr ttntn btwn thngs.
      </p>
      <p>
       Avd mtngs. Srsly. Thy fll p r dys wtht bng prdctv.
      </p>
      <p>
       Sngl-tsk nstd f mlt-tsk. Fcs n mprtnt thngs rthr thn  bnch f lttl thngs. If y gt cght p pnng nw tbs t rd, bkmrk thm ltr wth dlcs r nstppr r sm thr srvc.
      </p>
      <p>
       And njy th pcflnss. Rlx, tk nps,
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2009/07/breathe/">
        brth
       </a>
       .
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        If y hv lttl cntrl
       </strong>
       : S hw mch f th bv y cn lrdy mplmnt — y mght gt frthr thn y thnk. Mppng t n dl dy, lmntng cmmtmnts, smplfyng yr t-d lst, sngl-tskng, clrng wy dstrctns nd ntrrptns … mst ppl cn d mst f ths thngs, r f nt mst thngs thn t lst  fw.
      </p>
      <p>
       Als, tlk t yr bss. Tll yr bss tht y’d lk t b mr “prdctv” nd tht th ntrrptns nd mtngs r gttng n th wy f ccmplshng mr mprtnt thngs. Tll yr bss wht y’d lk t ccmplsh, nd wht y’d lk t chng bt yr schdl. Wrk t  cmprms.
      </p>
      <p>
       Als, thnk bt chngng jbs, f y rlly hv n cntrl. Ths s  lngr-trm chng, bvsly, bt t’s pssbl, nd myb vn dsrbl. Smthng t cnsdr, t lst.
      </p>
      <p>
       In th nd, whtvr chngs y mk, y cn b lss bsy smply by chngng yr mndst, t n whr y lv n th prsnt rthr thn lwys thnkng bt thr thngs. Slw dwn, brth, njy vry mmnt. Lrn t fcs n wht’s n frnt f y, nd fnd pc n whtvr y d.
      </p>
      <p>
       Thn rs yr fst gnst th wrld n vctry nd lgh qtly, hvng btn ths bsy bsy wrld.
      </p>
      <p>
